+  // DOSKUTSU patch 0048 (Phase 9 wave 6 Lever 2 Approach B): try the
+  // hand-rolled 16×16 fast path before queuing through SDL_RenderTexture.
+  // _try_fast_blit_16x16 returns true on success (drawn directly to
